org.qbroker.monitor

Class ScriptLauncher

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.qbroker.monitor.Monitor
      • org.qbroker.monitor.ScriptLauncher
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MonitorAction, MonitorReport

    public class ScriptLauncher
extends Monitor
    ScriptLauncher launches a script outside JVM and parses its stdout for patterns. It supports time dependent command with __MM____dd__.
    Author:
    yannanlu@yahoo.com
